{"tid":917100,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[力保不失]湯洛雯：與鄭子邦不過電 單身無拍拖","createTime":"2018-11-26T07:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T11:50:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"8562ecf548d9244954b6272ef8977d267021a4be","tid":917100,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20181126/s00092/f966d5bf095b4ce47a90a460fef561da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20181126%2Fs00092%2Ff966d5bf095b4ce47a90a460fef561da.jpg&h=bc8d24c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【明報專訊】湯洛雯最近被偷拍與姚子羚前男友鄭子邦在夜店態度親暱，因而傳出二人拍拖；昨日湯洛雯出席商場聖誕活動揭幕禮，全程笑容滿面兼表情多多，似乎心情不錯。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔開心驚被外界誤解</strong><br />\n<br />\n她表示今年單身過聖誕，目前狀况是宇宙無敵單身，未有拍拖，<strong>「報道說他（鄭子邦）追求我，不是事實。當晚是參加朋友生日飯局後，一班人包括莊思明、龔嘉欣到莊思敏所開的夜店坐，鄭子邦都在場。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當晚的相片完全是角度問題，因地方狹窄，大家站得很近，卻不是報道所講貼住身，我完全沒感受到被對方摸到」</span></span></strong>。二人沒為緋聞感尷尬，但身為女仔的湯洛雯對報道感不開心及不喜歡，驚外界對她有誤解便不好。<br />\n<br />\n無懼嚇怕其他追求者<br />\n<br />\n湯洛雯斬釘截鐵稱不會跟鄭子邦過電，目前專心工作，沒發展對象。湯洛雯再次劃清界線，「跟他有共同朋友，只見過幾次面，報道後也沒聯絡。無發展可能，因自己感覺到是好朋友相處，不是那種感覺」。她明白在娛樂圈工作易惹緋聞，不擔心嚇怕其他追求者。正在拍新劇《機場特警》，她希望聖誕節有假期，陪家人到瑞士旅行過節。她笑言會游說擁有好身材的妹妹穿三點式在冰天雪地浸溫泉，上載到社交平台分享。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林蘊兒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20181126/s00016/1543170704001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181126%2Fs00016%2F1543170704001&d=ihKXy5AFm8UklAqt1nq4ZUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b42b500c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181126%2Fs00016%2F1543170704001&h=d931222c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20181126/s00016/1543170704001</a><br />\n<br />\n冇蝕底到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5c78974b380466f6821c8ce26a2bce200e18b2","tid":917100,"uid":12754,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"比足錢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb46d8830e73244d17e43e67cb8f240960831d9","tid":917100,"uid":32282,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你信丫?"},{"pid":"0d406d3084374f5ad90a256ec90ccdf36e5fc0bf","tid":917100,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"bdb46d8830e73244d17e43e67cb8f240960831d9","tid":917100,"uid":32282,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你信丫?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"信<br />\n點解唔信?"},{"pid":"2f17eb39dc2110ecdfc768f1ae4c4fd6cbdd8397","tid":917100,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e5c78974b380466f6821c8ce26a2bce200e18b2","tid":917100,"uid":12754,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"比足錢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"含血噴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fb4042e12d6a2d7ce60f2f45d2fb8f7f2bb6b4","tid":917100,"uid":222907,"like":113,"disli